# This file is just a reminder — delete it when your paths are configured.
#
# When running CMake (via VS 2022 or cmake-gui), set these variables:
#
#   CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH = C:/Qt/6.8.x/msvc2022_64
#   OpenCV_DIR        = C:/opencv/build
#
# In VS 2022: Project > CMake Settings > CMake variables and cache
# Or add to CMakePresets.json (preferred for team sharing).
